      <h1>Anabolic Resistance Explained<br><span class="green">(Why Protein Needs Change After 40)</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">This is the biological mechanism behind every recommendation on this site — and why the advice you followed at 30 no longer produces the same results.</p>
